QuestData.Title: The Big Haul
QuestData.Description: Ey commander, fancy runnin' inta ya out here!$B$BTha garrison's got plenty a hungry mouths ta feed, with more folks comin' by every day.$B$BWe're really gonna need a big haul o' meat ta keep everyone happy.$B$BWouldya care ta lend us a hand? It'll be faster work with an extra pair a hands.
QuestData.CompletionText: Have ya seen tha size a these beasts?
QuestData.RewardText: Brilliant, just brilliant! Ay've never seen such a haul in my entire life!$B$BGet tha wagons ready. We're eatin' well tonight!
